data.description: Gorgeous 4/5 bedroom home! Family room open to kitchen, gas fireplace, vaulted ceiling. Pella windows. Master bedroom on main level w/ sitting area, vaulted ceiling, and walk in closet. Library/office w/ Murphy bed, private bath and closet. Jennaire cooktop in kitchen, built in oven, pantry, and island has electric. Large game room downstairs. 2 laundry areas, central vac unit. Large deck w/ wonderful view of wooded lot and lake. Walk-out basement w/ unfinished room for storage. 3 car tandem garage.
